  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A descriptive study to characterize clinical, radiological, lung function and quality of life
      alterations in patients who survived a severe or critical disease caused by SARS-COV-2 virus,
      who were treated in the intensive care unit of a high complexity institution in Cali,
      Colombia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
