  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients with a severe or critical disease caused by SARS-COV-2 infection who were treated
        at the ICU of Fundación Valle del Lili and were alive at 6 months of hospital discharge.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ≥ 19 years old who had a positive test for SARS-COV-2 virus

          -  Patients with a severe and critical disease by SARS-COV-2, who were treated at the ICU
             of Fundación Valle del Lili, and survived

          -  Patients with chest radiography or CT scan at admission to the hospital

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who do not sign informed consent.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
